cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SI, cs.CE 

The paper presents a data-driven approach for learning, modeling, and predicting phase segregation using conditional generative convolutional neural networks. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper involves the use of deep learning models (cs.AI) and focuses on the prediction of physical phenomena (cs.SI). Finally, the paper also involves the design and optimization of chemical systems (cs.CE).
